token_lists.title: "Copyminting" the Artist
token_lists.description:
This series is a creative coding exercise where I try to replicate an artists artwork as close as possible to the original.

All works are a collaboration between myself and the artist. They are 1/1 and all the proceeds will go towards a non profit / charity of the artists choice.

The process is documented on twitter, and you can access a link to each tweet by clicking on the `custom license` which should contain the link to the twitter thread where I explore the process.
